===Etymology 2===
Perhaps from the [[Polari]] slang word {{m|en|balonie}}. Alternatively, perhaps simply from {{m|en|bologna||sausage}}, possibly used as a [[minced oath]] for {{m|en|bullshit}}.

====Alternative forms====
* {{l|en|balonie}} {{qualifier|UK}}
* {{l|en|boloney}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{lb|en|uncountable|chiefly|US|slang}} [[nonsense|Nonsense]].
#: ''That's a bunch of '''baloney'''! I don't believe one word!''

=====Usage notes=====
Sometimes used in the rhyme ''phony baloney''.

